{"tid":924456,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【睇幾時害死人】消防處「任何人」落區教百人 CPR 及 AED","createTime":"2018-12-02T06:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T07:37:57.000Z","uid":37661,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"baeefd6bb156e6b4c84380125e58d14f4e098a85","tid":924456,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T06:22:38.000Z","msg":"真人示範！「任何仁」現身急救講座 百人跟住學CPR勁壯觀<br />\n<br />\n18分鐘前<br />\n即時要聞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n消防處早前推出真人扮演的「任何仁」，宣傳任何人都可救人的訊息，隨即在網上爆紅。消防處昨晚在其facebook專頁貼圖，指在其社區心肺復甦法及除顫器教育講座中，「任何仁」親身落場教授近百人CPR（心肺復甦法）技術的實況。有網民更留言指「任何仁」非常親民，亦有錯過活動的網民表示想報名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181202/large/1543728623_3ecb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181202%2Flarge%2F1543728623_3ecb.jpg&h=5d2328db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「任何仁」現身社區心肺復甦法及除顫器教育講座。消防處fb專頁圖片(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181202/large/1543728623_85d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181202%2Flarge%2F1543728623_85d2.jpg&h=f651b7d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「任何仁」親身落場教授近百人CPR技術的實況。消防處fb專頁圖片(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消防處fb專頁以「跟指引 學應急 任何人都得」為題，貼上其講座的現場照片，「『任何仁』多謝咁多熱心嘅市民嚟學 CPR 同 AED，仲一齊睇埋佢示範點樣跟住『調派後指引』去幫啲傷病者」，重申救人最緊要夠膽，無論跟住調派後指引做，或上堂學識CPR同AED，「有需要時，任何人都可以出手救人！」<br />\n<br />\n帖文附上hastag「#跟隨指引做」、「#敢就救到人」、「#未曾上課心驚驚」及「#上咗一課淡淡定」等等。有相信是參與講座的網民表示「任何仁」非常親民，亦有不少網民希望報名。該帖已獲逾1,300人讚好或「畀心心」等。<br />\n<br />\n消防處網頁資料顯示，今次社區心肺復甦法及除顫器教育講座的目的是精簡地向公眾人士講解基本的心肺復甦法和除顫器知識。講座後有體驗環節，供參加者嘗試施行心外壓及操作不同型號的除顫器。講座約為2小時，對象為12歲以上公眾人士（16歲以下人士必須由成人陪同出席），費用全免。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181202/58982896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181202%2F58982896&d=C1EOyJXh6EOFMYx1wJdv%2FWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=af151242\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181202%2F58982896&h=99659c37\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181202/58982896</a>"},{"pid":"d6de158e4e0ad9cdce59a49495b8ecc3ed43e7c0","tid":924456,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T06:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f575efc90e39301753b02847f8adb4ce71116e1","tid":924456,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c02c2b8d0660adb012441daeeccfb605b49684","tid":924456,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T07:24:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46abf310e43ca4026eff34c31bbe545c77c03d9d","tid":924456,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T07:37:57.000Z","msg":"方向報有冇出嚟屌消防，話會害死人呢?"}]}